Missing Value plot

Source: R/vmro.R
plotcombn.Rd

Plot of Missing Value combinations

Usage

plotcombn(obj)

Arguments

obj

a calcmissing object

Value

summarised info for plot

Author

Junjie Zeng

Examples

plotcombn(census.at.school.5000[, 10:25])
